## Instructions
Recommend an ordered certification path (3-5 certifications) that:
1. Starts with the user's current skill level
2. Builds skills progressively
3. Aligns with their stated role and goal
4. Considers prerequisite dependencies

Respond ONLY with a JSON object. No markdown, no preamble:
{
  "steps": [
    {
      "certificationId": "string",
      "order": 1,
      "rationale": "Why this first (2 sentences)",
      "estimatedWeeks": 6
    }
  ],
  "aiRationale": "Overall path explanation (3-4 sentences)"
}
